{"type": "article", "id": 25073, "title": "可放手机的卷纸架", "description": "", "date": "2016-04-07T07:11:00Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 6, "praise_count": 92, "image": "img/article/article_show/201607031238007JRuMl5NYTGAU1Zx.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">不少人都有将手机掉进厕所里的经历，在卷纸架上增加一个放手机的平台是再正常不过的。这组卷纸架的设计来自美国设计公司 Axis Design，放卷纸的轴心上连着一个与地面平行的平台，只在平台外增加了一个很浅的挡板，整体设计简洁干净而没有多余的地方。<a href=\"http://www.axisdesign.com/\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a><br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703123758J8uaGws45RHfvZT9.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.74952381\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607031237582QeOtcvSamUGLPyu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703123759HgK1OA9nSrRzDdPY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703123759WENlvKJXOQo5cwiY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}